### What’s included
- Floors `0..N-1` (default 10), elevators default 4
- Hall call buttons:
  - Bottom floor: up only
  - Top floor: down only
  - Middle floors: both
- In-elevator destination buttons for every floor
- All elevators start idle at floor 0
- Animated movement floor-by-floor
- Dispatching logic:
  - Closest idle elevator gets hall request first
  - If no idle, compatible moving elevator may take it
  - Otherwise request is queued and reassigned when possible
- Direction behavior:
  - Elevator continues current direction until that direction’s requests are done (or reaches boundary), then may reverse
- Status panel showing each elevator’s floor/state/targets + queued hall calls
- `index.html` includes model/tool/provider info from `info.json` under title

### Build verification
